values:
&nbsp;The year is 2007. There has been 2007 years since the birth of christ. Long time for people to still talk about someone.
I would presume I am not nearly as important as Jesus though. Based purely on how long it took many people to forget about me. Yup, it's true legends die, even the living legends. In the three short years since my last actual post I have gone thorugh manycircumstances and explianing the differences and occurences would be a waste of everyones time. The most major event though is some thing I may reference from time to time, which is the recent year I spent abroad in Germany. It went like this, imagine life being almost unbearable everyday, then all of a sudden everything is exactly how you want it to be. You have everything you need to be happy. Then after and a little while, just enough time for your new life to soak in, you leave it, not because it is a choice but because there is no choice. And when that life ends it is replaced with a world that has forgotten and does not care to ever recall the past which took so much work to build. That was the last year few years for me.
Now, don't get me wrong, I am fully aware that no one is reading this. I hold no dilusions of my own importance.&nbsp;
Since my truimphant and uncelebrated return I have been working towards rebuilding a former life without the negatives that it had. Well, all I could find where the negatives really, and hardly and of the people I knew could I call a friend.&nbsp;
Life goes on though, so, big deal. I learned a lot in life and one of those things is that I shouldn't give a damn. So, yeah, I dont give damn.&nbsp;


So damn it all.
